{"tid":2100813,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"韓聯社: 首爾市長朴元淳疑留下遺言失蹤　女兒報案 (18:13)","createTime":"2020-07-09T10:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T10:37:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2a35a5d062799af2fd96caf8946c0a35b6270c9a","tid":2100813,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:14:46.000Z","msg":"韓國首爾市長朴元淳的女兒當地時間今午（9日）約5時向警方報案，稱父親4、5小時前留下類似遺言後離家失蹤，目前手機關掉，警方正派人及出動無人機搜尋朴元淳下落。首爾市政府表示，朴元淳因身體不適沒有上班，市政府正在了解情況。<br />\n<br />\n64歲的朴元淳曾是人權律師，2011年當選首爾市長，2014、2018年連任。<br />\n<br />\n（韓聯社）"},{"pid":"1446ab57ce12fbb4c3e63725eb11b9882bfb2142","tid":2100813,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:16:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200709/XFQ7PON5YNCJU5NSRRX4OKHT2I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200709%2FXFQ7PON5YNCJU5NSRRX4OKHT2I%2F&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=bd0f2b08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200709%2FXFQ7PON5YNCJU5NSRRX4OKHT2I%2F&h=efc51b05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200709/XFQ7PON5YNCJU5NSRRX4OKHT2I/</a>"},{"pid":"45b0b8863bd33ef7d625c40a8661551a60c3caf4","tid":2100813,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:17:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1bee04c8e34cd7571b379f93142bb8b5b1a5c4","tid":2100813,"uid":206644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:17:35.000Z","msg":"綁架？"},{"pid":"310686a68e201f4c2160091f7e32af7bed7aab64","tid":2100813,"uid":232077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s